{
  "stem": "10587.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- I think the learning ceased to exist.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was bar mitzvah'd in the basement of my grandfather's house, and-- and many people came.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was not-- never the same as what would have really happened in our main-- in our temple, main sanctuary.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] sorry--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- I was-- I studied very hard because I want my parents to be proud of me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I also wanted to do a good job, because the-- of-- of what has been happening, to continue with my-- to carry on my-- my Jewish tradition.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so I worked harder and I-- I struggled, and I-- I don't personally remember.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I was told that I did a very good job.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my parents were very proud of me for doing what I did.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it was with candle lights, or-- and-- and those-- those-- the lights that you have with gasoline.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A gas lamp with the cylinder, glass cylinder.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and-- not actually gas, but it was gasoline type, you know, like, they call it naphtha, I remember, in Polish.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's how I remember having my bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Top secret, in top secret.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had guards standing outside that were not quite visible to make sure that the Germans, because we would have to disperse because they would have probably arrested a lot of people, and-- and they would have beaten a lot of people as well.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know if they would have killed anybody at that time, but they would definitely do a lot of harm.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I really don't remember exactly how we got there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think we-- we must have gone by train.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
